properties.areaDesc: Eastern Sawatch Mountains above 11000 Ft; Western Mosquito Range/East Lake County Above 11000 Ft
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 15 at 2:26PM MST until February 17 at 8:00AM MST by NWS Pueblo CO
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 5 to 10
inches. Winds gusting as high 50 to 60 mph.

* WHERE...Western Mosquito Range, East Lake County Above 11000
Feet, and the Eastern Sawatch Mountains Above 11000 Feet.

* WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to 8 AM MST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult. Areas of blowing snow
could significantly reduce visibility. The cold wind chills as
low as 20 below zero could cause frostbite on exposed skin in as
little as 30 minutes.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM THIS EVENING TO 8 AM MST MONDAY
